{"tid":587260,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我最討厭既角色就係做家姐","createTime":"2018-03-10T09:33:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-11T08:30:56.000Z","uid":61766,"like":50,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"a9b738c7bea141ab7c4a49513291f5099419af2e","tid":587260,"uid":61766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T09:33:44.000Z","msg":"我做咩都係錯<br />\n總之同細妹哎交<br />\n所有屋企人第一句就係<br />\n你讓下佢啦<br />\n<br />\n放假朝早都被佢嘈醒<br />\n訓唔返好燥底<br />\n叫佢唔好喺房化妝呀夾佢個死人頭<br />\n出去廁所整<br />\n我媽竟然話我咁醒訓幫唔到我<br />\n讓下佢啦一場姊妹<br />\n<br />\n買返屋企既零食<br />\n佢完全無問過就食咗<br />\n又係呢句<br />\n讓下佢啦一場姊妹<br />\n<br />\n無問過我又攞我啲衫褲去著<br />\n當然又係呢句<br />\n讓下佢啦一場姊妹<br />\n<br />\n我唔想有呢個妹架<br />\n我揀架咩？<br />\n我想出世先架？<br />\n讓讓讓<br />\n不如讓俾你做家姐好無"},{"pid":"9ac2b91026c0baaa8a27c8e5a85d12f74b58a782","tid":587260,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T09:35:41.000Z","msg":"唔好嬲啦家姐"},{"pid":"ce4c9466a57d60aba4ce631744262effba6cb82c","tid":587260,"uid":38904,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T09:35:59.000Z","msg":"只有濕尻老豆老母先會有依啲諗法<br />\n利申 阿哥, 好彩老豆老母冇噉諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b0959c24837ad2a96fd43bb03e7d03451ef4a08","tid":587260,"uid":74262,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T09:38:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"86a9e70caf44ee58fc37873fdef284b1e13aad45","tid":587260,"uid":147770,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T09:41:14.000Z","msg":"有個咁既呀媽唔怪得你呀妹咁撚賤"},{"pid":"a51a64159d47404de1cec6298554baac87b3f732","tid":587260,"uid":14046,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T10:01:59.000Z","msg":"係我就仆街啲<br />\n用多啲細妹既野<br />\n讓下啦一家人嘛"},{"pid":"e842abec992697b9eaf5627e9e1ebe7a92cdfe7b","tid":587260,"uid":61766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a51a64159d47404de1cec6298554baac87b3f732","tid":587260,"uid":14046,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-1